portation such as the Metro Line and several bus routes are located nearby. In addition there's also Uber and other similar services. The home is located near several major freeways so there's easy access to all the areas of Los Angeles.\n\nThe apartment includes a 6 pot/pan cookware set, complete dish sets, stainless steel utensils, bake-ware, toaster, microwave, coffeemaker as well as all other amenities. \n\nPak N Play sets as well as high chairs are available by request.  A rental fee of 15 USD applies to each for the entire trip.  Air mattresses and extra sheet sets are also available  for a rental fee of 25 USD each for the entire trip.\n\nFor stays longer than 13 days additional cleaning fees will apply.  An additional maid service visit will be required.",
