                "name": "Heart of WEHO! Sunny & Tre",
                "description": "This trendy 1 bedroom/1 bath is perfect for play or work. The space is perfectly decorated and will make you feel at home the moment you walk through the door. You'll appreciate the 65 inch smart TV in the living area, fully-equipped kitchen, an A/C in living area and bedroom and your own private balcony. Of course, it also comes with free WiFi , free parking in the garage for a regular sized vehicle, and great vibes to ensure a great trip in Los Angeles!\n\nWith self check-in and a completely private unit, we want to make your getaway the easiest experience  it can be. \n\nAs soon as you walk up the stairs and open the door to this 1bed/1bath, you'll find the living space features a comfortable seating area, a 65 inch smart TV (no cable), AC, and a desk area perfect for a workspace. The kitchen includes everything you need to cook at home and a dining area for enjoying a meal.\n\nThere is one full bathroom and one spacious bedroom with a comfortable queen bed and ample closet space. The bedroom also features your own private balcony.\n\nWhen you're ready to wander out, you'll find a Whole Foods a few blocks away and even a liquor store at the corner. The location is an inexpensive Uber ride to the many great clubs and restaurants in West Hollywood. For those coming with a rental car or bringing your own, please note, we provide one parking space for a regular sized vehicle only (nothing oversized). The flat comes with a free wifi.\n\nThis home is yours for your stay!\n\nWe do not provide access to a mailbox. If any questions about receiving mail and options for that, please ask.\n\nLaundry is shared by building and is on property, not in unit. Guests don’t have access to mailbox. We provide 1 parking spot for a regular sized vehicle.",
