                "airbnb_neighborhood_id": 48424,
                "name": "High Rise apt with Stunning view",
                "description": "❗️LOCATED IN KOREA-TOWN IN LOS ANGELES❗️\nTHE APPROX ADDRESS IS DISCLOSED FOR THE PRIVACY OF MY PAST CURRENT & UPCOMING GUESTS\n\nFor any traveler seeking an unforgettable experience in Los Angeles, this luxurious accommodation is an absolute must. Situated within a convenient 3-6 mile radius, you'll find an array of captivating attractions including Hollywood, Beverly Hills, Universal studio, the Crypto Center, and Downtown LA.\n\nWelcome to our exquisite apartment, nestled in the heart of Los Angeles. Prepare to be enchanted by this magnificent haven that offers an unparalleled experience for every traveler.\n\nStep inside and be mesmerized by the sweeping 180-degree views that span the horizon. From the majestic mountains to the iconic Hollywood sign, immerse yourself in the beauty that surrounds you.\n\nSavor the lively atmosphere of our meticulously crafted apartment. Every detail has been thoughtfully selected to create a space that radiates elegance and sophistication. Delight in the vibrant and welcoming ambiance that greets you at every corner.\n\nRelax in the embrace of our luxurious queen-size bed, featuring a plush, cloud-like mattress. Drift into a peaceful sleep under the gentle touch of our premium linens, ensuring a night of pure comfort and renewal.\n\nConvenience is paramount, and our secure parking garage provides an assigned spot for your vehicle, offering peace of mind throughout your stay.\n\nEscape the urban hustle with a leisurely 20-minute drive to the pristine beaches, where you can bask in the sun and immerse yourself in the relaxed coastal atmosphere.\n\nDon’t miss out on this chance to indulge in luxury and comfort. Reserve your stay now and let us be your hosts, where every moment is tailored to surpass your expectations.\n\nFree parking space in the parking garage\n﻿Simple and fast self check in\n﻿Fully Renovated from top to bottom\n﻿All Brand New Appliances\n﻿Hardwood Floor\n﻿Smoke-Free and Quiet Community\n﻿Get the entire unit\n﻿Smart TV (Netflix & other streaming available)\n﻿Free and Fast WIFI!!!!!\n﻿Gorgeous Modern King Bed\n﻿Chic and Modern Design\n﻿﻿Laundry in building\n﻿Full Kitchen\n﻿Refrigerator\n﻿Dishwasher, Microwave\n﻿Toaster, Coffee Maker\n﻿Pot, Pan, Dishes, Silverware, Towels, Hair Dryer, Iron and Ironing Board all provided\n﻿Shampoo & Conditioner\n﻿central A.C. & Heater in-Unit\nAs our valued guest, you'll have access to a range of luxurious amenities that are designed to make your stay as comfortable and enjoyable as possible.\nTake a dip in the sparkling pool, unwind in the relaxing hot tub, and stay active in our state-of-the-art gym. And when it's time to satisfy your hunger, head to the BBQ area and cook up a delicious meal to enjoy in the sun.\n\nWelcome to our cozy home! We aim to make your stay as comfortable and enjoyable as possible. Here’s how we’ll interact with you during your stay:\n\nCheck-In and Check-Out:\nWe offer flexible self-check-in with a key entry system. You will receive detailed instructions prior to your arrival. Check-in is anytime after 4 PM, and check-out is by 11 AM.\n\nCommunication:\nWe believe in giving our guests their space to relax, but we’re always just a message or call away if you need us. Feel free to reach out through the Airbnb app for any questions or concerns. We typically respond within an half hour.\n\nDuring Your Stay:\nWhile we respect your privacy, we are happy to assist with any recommendations or needs you might have. Whether you need tips on local attractions, restaurant recommendations, or help with the amenities, we’re here to help.\n\nEmergency Contact:\nIn case of any urgent issues, you can reach us on our mobile number 24/7. We want to ensure that any problems are resolved quickly so you can enjoy your stay without any interruptions.\n\nAs part of our commitment to cleanliness, we have a strict no shoes policy in all our units. This means you can book with confidence, knowing that your stay will be fresh, clean, and comfortable. So whether you're here for business or pleasure, you can relax and unwind in a space that feels like home.",
