                "description": "Fully furnished 850+ square feet private Hollywood Apartment with Wi-Fi and amenities. 40\" LCD TV. Pool view. Full size kitchen.\n\nMinimum 31 nights or more (No Tax)\n\nWalking distance to Walk of Fame, Hollywood/Highland Metro, McDonald's, Ralph's Grocery Store, Target, Best Buy, StarBucks at WeHo Gateway Mall.\n\nFree street parking is usually easy to find. Underground security gated parking is available for $10/night cash. Please inquire when booking if you are interested.   \n\nYou will have the entire place to yourself and will NOT be sharing the space with anyone else. There are no personal items in the unit belonging to the owner of the apartment so feel free to use all the items and appliances provided.\n\nThis large one bedroom apartment is set-up to accommodate 3 guests.\n\nBright, sunny, spacious, with pool view. \nFull size bed (2 people) \nSofa bed (1 person) \n\nFully Equipped Kitchen:\nRefrigerator\nGas stove\nToaster \nMicrowave \nDishes \nUtensils (Forks, spoons, knives, Etc.)\nKitchen cookware (Pots, pans, spatula, etc)\n\nBathroom amenities such as towels, shampoo and soap are provided.\n\nOther Amenities\nWireless Internet\nAir Conditioner \nIron/Iron Board\nHair Dryer\nPool\nBuilding Elevator\nBuilding has on-site laundry room (Coin operated Washer and Dryer)\n\nAll towels and sheets are washed, and sinks, tub and toilet are all cleaned before check-in! \n\nThis is a NON-SMOKING apartment and building. It is very important to understand that the security deposit will be forfeited if you smoke inside of the apartment or building.\n\nThis is a private apartment with its own entrance. You will be given keys to the front door of the apartment building, the apartment itself and the laundry room (please remember to return the keys to the host during the check-out walk through).\n\nWe will be here to greet the guests and give a walk through of the apartment building.\n\nCheck-in time is 4 PM or after\nCheck-out time is 11 AM or earlier\n\nFree street parking is usually easy to find but make sure to read all city parking signs before you park. Underground security gated parking is available for $10/night cash.",
